attributes.value:
*
Mint - Math interoperability standard types.

Defines basic math types useful for computer graphics.
Designed to serve as an interoperability standard between libraries.
*/

defs.name: Quaternion
defs.docs:
Standard quaternion represented by the scalar and vector parts.
 Useful for representing rotation in 3D space.
 Corresponds to a right-handed rotation matrix.

attributes.value: / Standard quaternion represented by the scalar and vector parts.
/ Useful for representing rotation in 3D space.
/ Corresponds to a right-handed rotation matrix.

defs.name: EulerAngles
defs.docs:
Abstract set of Euler angles in 3D space. The basis of angles
 is defined by the generic parameter `B`.

attributes.value: / Abstract set of Euler angles in 3D space. The basis of angles
/ is defined by the generic parameter `B`.
/ Note: there are multiple notations of Euler angles. They are
/   - intrinsic (also known as "Tait-Bryan angles"): rotate around local axis
/   - extrinsic (also known as "Proper Euler angles"): rotate around world axis
/ For each interpretation, different axis may be chosen in different order.

defs.name: a
defs.docs: First angle of rotation in range [-pi, pi] (_pitch_).

attributes.value: / First angle of rotation in range [-pi, pi] (_pitch_).

defs.name: b
defs.docs: Second angle of rotation around in range [-pi/2, pi/2] (_yaw_).

attributes.value: / Second angle of rotation around in range [-pi/2, pi/2] (_yaw_).

defs.name: c
defs.docs: Third angle of rotation in range [-pi, pi] (_roll_).

attributes.value: / Third angle of rotation in range [-pi, pi] (_roll_).

defs.name: IntraXYZ
defs.docs: Intrinsic rotation around X, then Y, then Z axis.

attributes.value: / Intrinsic rotation around X, then Y, then Z axis.

defs.name: IntraZXZ
defs.docs: Intrinsic rotation around Z, then X, then Z axis.

attributes.value: / Intrinsic rotation around Z, then X, then Z axis.

defs.name: IntraZYX
defs.docs: Intrinsic rotation around Z, then Y, then X axis.

attributes.value: / Intrinsic rotation around Z, then Y, then X axis.

defs.name: ExtraXYZ
defs.docs: Extrinsic rotation around X, then Y, then Z axis.

attributes.value: / Extrinsic rotation around X, then Y, then Z axis.

defs.name: ExtraZXZ
defs.docs: Extrinsic rotation around Z, then X, then Z axis.

attributes.value: / Extrinsic rotation around Z, then X, then Z axis.

defs.name: ExtraZYX
defs.docs: Extrinsic rotation around Z, then Y, then X axis.
